==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Permian
<hw>Per"mi*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. a.</pos> <ety>[From the
ancient kingdom of <ets>Permia</ets>, where the Permian formation
exists.]</ety> <fld>(Geol.)</fld> <def>Belonging or relating to the
period, and also to the formation, next following the Carboniferous, and
regarded as closing the Carboniferous age and Paleozoic era.</def> --
<def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>The Permian period. See <xex>Chart</xex> of
<er>Geology</er>.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Permians</ent>⟦br⟧
